ssisting patients to ambulate using a transfer belt. The tutorial covers preparation, communication, application of the transfer belt, and the ambulation process itself. By the end of this tutorial, participants will be able to: \n- Remember the necessary steps and safety protocols for using a transfer belt. \n- Understand the importance of proper transfer techniques in patient safety. \n- Apply the correct method to secure the transfer belt and assist patients in ambulation. \n- Analyze the patient's condition and environment to adjust the approach as needed. \n- Evaluate their technique to ensure it adheres to best practices and safety standards. \n- Create a safe and supportive environment for patients during ambulation using a transfer belt. \n\nThis comprehensive approach ensures CNAs are well-prepared to assist patients with proper care efficiently and compassionately in real-world clinical settings. ", "short_description": "Learn the essential skill of safely assisting patients to ambulate using a transfer belt."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/privacy-policy.html", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Holo Pundits", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.holopundits.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1043107547362485"}, {"id": "478089301798119"}, {"id": "514087707868786"}], "external_subscription_type": "REQUIRED_FOR_SOME_CONTENT", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE